This project contains configuration files for ESPHome-based monitoring
and control of photovoltaic inverters via Modbus RTU communication.

Project Repository: https://github.com/Lewa-Reka/esphome-pv-inverter 

================================================================================
This project is built upon the ESPHome platform.
ESPHome is a framework for controlling ESP8266/ESP32 devices.
Copyright (c) 2019 ESPHome

